name: Boss
description:
Printed on to a Professional A4 Heat Transfer paper, then transferred on to a top quality, highly reputable, white Gildan Heavy T-shirt.


Buy one size bigger and roll up your sleeves for that 'Oversized' look!


Garment care:  Wash inside-out on a low temperature to avoid losing the print quality.


Please note that the size and positioning of the print may differ slightly to that shown in the picture as all of our printed products are hand-made to order.  We cannot offer refunds as our printed products are all made to order, making each one of them unique.


Check us out on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PosseClothing
